text: Bar Rock is a barren rock within Massachusetts Bay, in Scituate, Massachusetts, USA. The rock is just east of the Scituate neighborhood of Minot, off the coast of Scituate Neck. More specifically, the rock is east of the Bailey's Causeway & Glades Road intersection.
